<%- include header.ejs %>
<div id="home-nav">
<%- include pub_navbar.ejs %>
</div>
<div class="splash-bg"></div>
<div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="splash-page">
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="/img/dogecache-logo.png" />
        </div>
        <h1>
          Welcome to Dogecache.
        </h1>

        <div class="description">
          Explore the world and find dogecoin.
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#e74c3c"> <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          Dogecache is inspired by the largely popular activity Geocaching, where people engage in a GPS-assisted scavenger hunt.
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#95a5a6"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          Like in Geocaching, you hunt for something in Dogecache. You're hunting for dogecoin.
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#3498db"> <i class="fa fa-globe"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          But it isn't just you. Everyone's in on it.
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#f1c40f">√ê</div>
        <div class="description">
          Look for dogecoin dispersed throughout the world. You'll be bound to find some - dogecoin dropped by others!
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#c0392b"><i class="fa fa-frown-o"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          Yes, you do have to drop some dogecoin, wherever you are, in order to scavenge for some around your area.
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#dddddd"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          But the more you drop, the bigger area you can search around you!
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#2ecc71"><i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          Whatever dogecoin you find in your area becomes yours!
        </div>

        <div class="header-icon" style="color:#d35400" >
          <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="description">
          What're you waiting for? Play now!
        </div>

        <div class="home-button-wrapper">
          <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
            <a type="button" class="home-button map-button" href="/map">
              <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
              Go to Map
            </a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a type="button" class="home-button login-button">
              <i class="fa fa-heart-o"></i>
              Sign in / Sign up
            </a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<%- include footer.ejs %>